WEBVTT

00:00:07.945 --> 00:00:11.031 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I came to Greece as an immigrant
when I was just 16 years old.

00:00:11.782 --> 00:00:13.993 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
Because of that, I never felt safe

00:00:13.993 --> 00:00:16.036 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
with people around me.

00:00:16.036 --> 00:00:18.038 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
At that time, I was renting

00:00:18.038 --> 00:00:20.875 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
an apartment from a man
who was studying the Bible

00:00:20.875 --> 00:00:22.918 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with one of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:00:24.086 --> 00:00:26.547 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
One day I joined the study,

00:00:26.547 --> 00:00:28.799 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the brother invited me to the convention.

00:00:30.551 --> 00:00:35.431 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was very cautious at the beginning,
but the brother seemed trustworthy.

00:00:37.641 --> 00:00:39.894 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I always had questions about the true God,

00:00:39.894 --> 00:00:43.522 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I wanted to learn more about Him,
so I decided to go.

00:00:44.982 --> 00:00:46.984 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In 2016,

00:00:46.984 --> 00:00:48.485 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I received an invitation

00:00:48.485 --> 00:00:49.987 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
from my son to attend

00:00:49.987 --> 00:00:51.906 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
the convention of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:00:51.906 --> 00:00:54.283 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
He was getting baptized at that convention,

00:00:54.283 --> 00:00:57.494 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it was important to him
for me to be there,

00:00:57.494 --> 00:00:59.538 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and so he asked me to go.

00:00:59.538 --> 00:01:03.375 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Even though I was very active
in another religion for 30 years,

00:01:03.375 --> 00:01:05.419 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I went in order to please him.

00:01:07.796 --> 00:01:12.801 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I learned the truth after I supplicated God
with all my strength

00:01:12.801 --> 00:01:14.845 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
because I was really lost.

00:01:14.845 --> 00:01:16.889 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
I asked for answers to questions

00:01:16.889 --> 00:01:18.807 line:10%,start position:50%,center align:center
that were yet unanswered.

00:01:18.807 --> 00:01:20.559 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And God answered me.

00:01:20.559 --> 00:01:24.897 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah gave me the answer
to my prayers when I found this.

00:01:24.897 --> 00:01:29.693 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This invitation, “Deliverance at Hand!,”
was the answer to my prayers.

00:01:31.528 --> 00:01:36.283 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Arriving there, at that convention,
I observed the crowd—many people.

00:01:36.283 --> 00:01:38.285 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Starting right at the parking lot,

00:01:39.328 --> 00:01:43.207 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
everything was organized;
people were entering in an orderly manner.

00:01:43.207 --> 00:01:46.043 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Inside the Assembly Hall,
everyone was very organized,

00:01:46.043 --> 00:01:48.629 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
well-dressed, very loving.

00:01:48.629 --> 00:01:51.340 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And when the convention began,

00:01:51.340 --> 00:01:55.511 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I saw such spiritual food
that I had never seen in my religion.

00:01:56.679 --> 00:01:59.598 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thirty years in a religion
—I thought I knew a lot,

00:01:59.598 --> 00:02:01.266 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but I didn’t know anything.

00:02:02.768 --> 00:02:05.521 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So I decided to study.

00:02:05.521 --> 00:02:09.775 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When I arrived at the convention,
I started watching the people.

00:02:09.775 --> 00:02:11.819 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Their faces were smiling.

00:02:11.819 --> 00:02:14.154 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They seemed to be happy.

00:02:14.154 --> 00:02:18.033 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There were men, women, and children
from different races and nationalities.

00:02:19.785 --> 00:02:23.330 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When they sang,
I could sense their true joy and unity.

00:02:26.417 --> 00:02:30.671 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
For the first time in my life,
I felt very safe.

00:02:30.671 --> 00:02:33.340 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was not in fear
of being taken advantage of.

00:02:35.384 --> 00:02:38.762 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Also, what I learned at that convention

00:02:38.762 --> 00:02:40.806 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
drew me to the true God.

00:02:42.433 --> 00:02:44.435 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I thought, ‘If all these people

00:02:44.435 --> 00:02:48.856 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘are truly happy and feel really safe
being part of this organization

00:02:48.856 --> 00:02:51.900 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‘—Jehovah’s organization—

00:02:51.900 --> 00:02:55.279 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
then, indeed,
this is what I was looking for.’

00:02:57.239 --> 00:03:00.451 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I went to the convention on Sunday.

00:03:00.451 --> 00:03:04.496 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was really warmly welcomed
by all the brothers and sisters there.

00:03:06.290 --> 00:03:09.793 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I listened to all of the morning program,

00:03:09.793 --> 00:03:13.630 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and at noon,
I recognized the sound of the truth.

00:03:13.630 --> 00:03:15.632 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was sure it was the truth.

00:03:17.092 --> 00:03:19.636 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I decided to become
one of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:03:19.636 --> 00:03:21.805 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I became one of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:03:21.805 --> 00:03:26.602 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I got baptized in 2017,
and now I serve as a pioneer.

00:03:27.561 --> 00:03:30.731 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My first study was the following Wednesday.

00:03:30.731 --> 00:03:33.484 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I was happy to get to know Jehovah.

00:03:33.484 --> 00:03:36.361 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now I am one of Jehovah’s Witnesses,

00:03:36.361 --> 00:03:41.325 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and as much as I can,
I participate in the invitation campaigns.

00:03:41.325 --> 00:03:44.828 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I really hope that it helps
many people to be delivered.

00:03:45.913 --> 00:03:49.792 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I started attending meetings
right after the convention.

00:03:49.792 --> 00:03:52.503 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I started a Bible study,
and eventually I got baptized

00:03:52.503 --> 00:03:54.630 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
as one of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

00:03:56.298 --> 00:03:58.509 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My mother, one of my brothers,

00:03:58.509 --> 00:04:01.470 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and my two sisters
are now serving Jehovah as well.

00:04:02.846 --> 00:04:05.808 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Later on, I got married to a faithful sister,

00:04:05.808 --> 00:04:08.811 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a very good wife,
and we serve Jehovah together.

00:04:09.770 --> 00:04:12.648 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
People need to feel safe,

00:04:12.648 --> 00:04:17.528 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and I know for sure that Jehovah’s
organization is the safest place you can be.

